videos.description: Nebraska's Jordy Tshimanga fakes out his defender in the post to get the hook shot to fall.
videos.headline: Tshimanga uses a great post move to find the basket

videos.description: Penn State head coach Patrick Chambers discusses Mike Watkins' defensive play in the 1st half.
videos.headline: Patrick Chambers on Mike Watkins' impact on the game in the 1st half

videos.description: Penn State's Shep Garner hits a pair of 3-pointers and his cousin, Flava Flav, cheers for him.
videos.headline: Flava Flav reacts to cousin's 3-pointers

videos.description: Nebraska's Glynn Waton Jr. knocks down a 3-pointer to tie the game with 56 seconds to go.
videos.headline: Nebraska 3-pointer ties game in final minute

videos.description: Penn State's Mike Watkins records his eighth block of the game to set the record for most blocks in a Big Ten Tournament game.
videos.headline: Watkins sets Big Ten Tournament for most blocks in a game
